pkg:outlineMarker.div:
  The next outlineMarker should be copyable.

copy=true



BEGIN {
	# XXX stupid hack for now.  needs to tee/log/etc
	if($PerlWrapper::BundlePath) {
		open(STDERR, '>', "/tmp/thout.$$.err");
		select STDERR; $| = 1;
		$SIG{__DIE__} = sub {
			warn $_[0];
			die $_[0];
		}
	}
}
# XXX why is this an ENV var? --Eric
# set par temp to data dir if it doesn't exist
$ENV{'Thout_lib'}='';
if ($ENV{'PAR_TEMP'}){
	$ENV{'Thout_lib'} = $ENV{'PAR_TEMP'}.'/inc/';
}

pkg:outlineMarker.pkg:outlineMarker:
These use a trick to hide the real source code, and display formatted source code.


  This example should work - uses renderchildren=false to hide cleaned-copyable code. 



